pingball.util

Class BidirectionalMap<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • pingball.util.BidirectionalMap<K,V>

  • public final class BidirectionalMap<K,V>
extends java.lang.Object
    A bidirectional Map. Rep invariant: A mapping occurs in forwardMapping if and only if the reverse mapping occurs in reverseMapping.
